Pros: 
- fun mix of genres and emotional rollercoaster;
- well-written dialogues;
- good music;
- answers some questions from previous games.

Cons: 
- shorter and less interactive (as far as I remember) than previous games;
- newer engine would be appreciated (Visuals are ok, but UI and resolution are bad). From one of community threads it seems that devs are already trying new engine for the next game.
